1. On je iste godine* istog* datuma rođen kao i ja. (He was born the same year and on the same date as me.)

2. Svi smo ostali istog* mišljenja oko toga. (We all stayed of the same opinion about that.)

3. Ona je još uvek istog* stava. (She is still of the same opinion.)

4. Njihov je plan bio istog* dana da pođu. (Their plan was to leave on the same day.)

5. Oni su čuli istog* čoveka kako govori. (They heard the same man speaking.)